summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 14499 entitled: "An ordinance authorizing and directing the Board of Public Works to complete the planking of 15th Avenue West, between Grand Boulevard and Ruffner Street, in the City of Seattle, as provided for by Ordinance No. 12358, creating Local Improvement District No. 1076 providing for the improvement of Grand Boulevard, et al, at the expense of the contractor for said improvement, and appropriating money therefor."
